{
  "text": "We intend to develop our approach to making good recommendations to users of our PTA system. We are currently implementing the mechanism for learning the request feature weights and hope to use this to further improve our recommendations. We intend to implement further techniques including Collaborative CBR and learning the local similarity measure (in the same manner as work done by Stahl [CITATION_1] ).",
  "citation_candidates": [
